    "description": "The Girl Who Sees is a point-and-click adventure and tactical RPG hybrid that explores WWII history and Philippine fantasy.  In 1945, a village girl Quina survives under Japanese occupation. She helps a dwarf translate a mysterious scroll in hopes it will explain why she sees Tagalog words wherever she turns. Aid both human and magical, fight mythical foes, and restore balance to the realm.<br> <br>Choose your gameplay style:<br>- Battle Mode: Level up by fighting in turn-based battles.<br>- Discovery Mode: Level up by answering trivia on Philippine culture, history, and lore.<br><br>This game was created through a crowdfunding campaign and through the support of the Filipinx-American community.<br><br><strong>EXPLORE MAGICAL MINDANAO</strong><br>Interact with Philippine mythical creatures, the humans in Quina's village, and the occupying soldiers. Complete tasks for them to gain experience and level up.<br><br><strong>LEARN TAGALOG WORDS</strong><br>Collect Tagalog words and build your dictionary to translate Tagalog sentences into English. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551480/extras/2eb13e0dc18e8a69d9b1d7952faf7a11.avif?t=1719545707\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PLAY STYLE: </strong><br>Throughout your quests, you will encounter ancient Filipino magical creatures hindering your way forward. <br><br><strong>BATTLE MODE </strong><br>In BATTLE MODE, fight against the mythical creatures with Edgar through turn-based battles. <br><br>Craft potions for the local albularya (shaman woman) to gain new special attacks. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551480/extras/9e4e00a29fe16469d57579d0d5364994.poster.avif?t=1719545707\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551480/extras/9e4e00a29fe16469d57579d0d5364994.mp4?t=1719545707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DISCOVERY MODE</strong><br>In DISCOVERY MODE, fight creatures by answering trivia questions on Philippine culture, history, and mythology. This play-style may be more suitable for educational settings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551480/extras/14b2520c21769d609c180a082c3de50c.avif?t=1719545707\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
